# Metadata for AI Explorer

## Project Information
- **Name**: AI Explorer
- **Package Name**: ai_explorer
- **Version**: 1.0.0+1
- **Description**: A Flutter application showcasing generative AI capabilities using GenUI and Firebase AI

## Repository
- **URL**: https://github.com/highlanderkev/ai-explorer
- **Issue Tracker**: https://github.com/highlanderkev/ai-explorer/issues

