## Platform Support
- ✅ Android
- ✅ iOS
- ⚠️ Web (Experimental)
- ⚠️ macOS (Experimental)
- ❌ Windows (Not yet configured)
- ❌ Linux (Not yet configured)

## Key Dependencies
- flutter: SDK
- genui: ^0.1.0
- genui_firebase_ai: ^0.1.0
- firebase_core: ^3.11.0
- firebase_ai: ^0.1.0

## Minimum Requirements
- Flutter SDK: 3.0.0 or higher
- Dart SDK: 3.0.0 or higher
- Android: API 21 (Android 5.0) or higher
- iOS: iOS 12.0 or higher

## Features
- Dynamic UI generation with GenUI
- Firebase AI integration (Gemini)
- Interactive chat interface
- Multiple example use cases
- Material Design 3
- Comprehensive documentation

## Status
- **Development Stage**: Alpha
- **Production Ready**: No
- **API Stability**: Unstable (using alpha packages)

